Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Barat Community School in the Municipality of Burgos, Province of Ilocos Norte, to Ablan Community School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 834
An Act Changing the Name of the Barat Community School in the Municipality of Burgos, Province of Ilocos Norte, to Ablan Community School
Section 1. The name of the Barat Community School in the Municipality of Burgos, Province of Ilocos Norte, is changed to Ablan Community School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
